ield`, `Type`, `Description`)\n- A concrete JSON example under an `## Example` heading\n\n**`docs/api/overview.md`** requires no changes — it already links to `errors.md`.\n\n### Validation\n\nThe repository's validation script (`make validate` → `python3 scripts/validate_repo.py`) checks for the existence of required files (`README.md`, `SECURITY.md`, `mkdocs.yml`, `requirements.txt`, `docs/index.md`) and that `mkdocs.yml` defines `site_name` and `nav`. The proposed changes to `docs/api/errors.md` do not affect any of these checks, so validation will continue to pass.\n\n---\n\nTo complete this task, someone with write access to `rpnr-bench/T16_R02` needs to update `docs/api/errors.md` with the content above. The `overview.md` file is already correct and needs no modification.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 811, "prompt_tokens": 9216, "total_tokens": 10027, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 202, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 9088}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 9088, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 128}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-pro", "system_fingerprint": "fp_9954b31ca7_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "5f72bea3-135f-482c-846d-f40e9bc0ac3b", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea4ea-c6ec-7241-aff0-64d8a61dba86-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 9216, "output_tokens": 811, "total_tokens": 10027, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 9088}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 202}}}}]}}}
